channel.title: Internet went down
channel.description:
I'm not trying to be a nub about this ima pretty experienced editor for my server... I know there is no possible way for some1 to see my origional source ect but the problem is about 5 days ago my dumb-@$$ stepdad f#@%ed up my router and basicly [u][i][b]I[/b][/i][/u] just got it fixed... For about a week i was editing my server adding things, deleting ect... So when i finially do get my internet fixed I do these things 1) Update my No-Ip DOC and go to no-ip.com and put in my new ip 2) Make sure everything in my server file is how it should be... I had realized something was wrong because when i go to start up my server normally it wouldnt go up... Everything goes exactly how it always has it says its running i check my IPs... Everythings right but noone can get on and I did check; my server is not online... Anyone know how to help? Does anyone know how to fix it? The compiler is working great nothing is wrong there and when i start up my server it doesn't give any extra messages besides
Starting Dragsxd Server on 0.0.0.0:43594
Thanks in advance to anyone that helps. Guys please post your ideas on how to fix this. I know sometimes you look at what other people have said and decide not to post so don't look =] Btw Dragsxd is my server =[] I am going to give everyone a download for it soon so you guys can use it =]. Some major things to add before its done though.
